text: Valentyn Kostyantynovych Symonenko (; born July 4, 1940) is a Ukrainian politician. Between 1996 and 2011 he was chairman of the Accounting Chamber of Ukraine. Accounting Chamber of Ukraine - official site For a short time in October 1992, he was the Acting Prime Minister of Ukraine. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Ukraine
